creator: 100%Game
descriptionHtml:
Use your imagination to match Emoji
In the game, you need to understand and imagine to match the correct Emoji. Just use your fingers to gently connect the different columns of Emoji, and you can win the game. This game is harder than you think, compare it with your friends and prove your ingenuity!
